ar por un lugar en las leaderboards online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/47788e55359fe2d2e9299479bf3181a9.poster.avif?t=1752800947\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/47788e55359fe2d2e9299479bf3181a9.webm?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/47788e55359fe2d2e9299479bf3181a9.mp4?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modo carrera y repetición</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >¿Quieres mejorar aún más tus tiempos? ¡Mira repeticiones de cualquier jugador en las tablas de clasificación y aprende sus estrategias! Desafía a sus fantasmas y lleva tus habilidades al límite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/675c79e3d8b2aecb04b388d6c4ac8f11.poster.avif?t=1752800947\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/675c79e3d8b2aecb04b388d6c4ac8f11.webm?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/675c79e3d8b2aecb04b388d6c4ac8f11.mp4?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Salta con estilo</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >En Leap Galaxy encontrarás una gran variedad de personajes jugables, cada uno con sus propias animaciones distintivas y encantadoras. ¿No te gustan los colores predeterminados? ¡No hay problema! Elige entre varias combinaciones de colores desbloqueables y encuentra la que mejor se adapte a tu estilo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/24fe7bcb6e06db5bfc02feb070e16c02.poster.avif?t=1752800947\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/24fe7bcb6e06db5bfc02feb070e16c02.webm?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/24fe7bcb6e06db5bfc02feb070e16c02.mp4?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
